cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD

This paper deals with object detection for autonomous vehicles using sensor fusion of color and lidar data. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a deep learning architecture for this task, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with handling adverse weather conditions, which could also fall under the software engineering (cs.SD) sub-category.
